**Breaking down the discussion so far:**

1. Core Review Service (Spring Boot)
This service will handle the main functionality around reviews for your e-commerce system. Here's a step-by-step guide for setting it up:

    a. Setup Spring Boot
    Use Spring Initializr to generate a Spring Boot project with the following dependencies:
    Spring Web: For building the REST API.
    Spring Data JPA: To interact with the SQL database.
    Spring MySQL , JDBC Driver
    b. Define the Review Entity
    
